    <title>Edge AI Inference Optimization for Industrial IoT Devices</title>
    <summary>We propose a lightweight quantization scheme for running deep neural
networks on resource-constrained edge devices in industrial settings, reducing
latency by 40% without significant accuracy loss.</summary>
